            }));</script>         <h1 id="pqv-title"> Product Summary: Shivsoft Kid Magic Spring Rainbow Bouncy Expandable Slinky Magic Toys Return Gift, Party Favours (Multi Coloured, Pack of 2) </h1>    <p id="pqv-byline">From Shivsoft</p>               <div class="a-section a-spacing-medium">  <p id="pqv-ratings" data-target="#averageCustomerReviews_feature_div" class="a-spacing-none">  3.7 out of 5 stars, 286 ratings </p> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-reviews-action" data-pqv-reviews-action="{}"> <a id="pqv-reviews" data-target="#customer-reviews_feature_div" class="a-link-normal" href="?ref=dp_product_quick_view#customer-reviews_feature_div"> Customer reviews </a> </span>   <p id="pqv-bought-in-last-month" data-target="#socialProofingAsinFaceout_feature_div" class="a-spacing-none">100+ viewed in past month</p>  </div>        <div class="a-section a-spacing-medium"> <h2 id="pqv-price"> Price </h2>             <p class="a-spacing-small">              <span class="a-text-bold"> One-time purchase: ₹189.00 </span>                  </p>                                                     <p id="pqv-price-vat-message" class="a-spacing-small">  Inclusive of all taxes  </p>           <p class="a-text-italic"> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-buybox-action" data-pqv-buybox-action="{}"> <a id="pqv-buybox" data-target="#buybox" class="a-link-normal" href="?ref=dp_product_quick_view#buybox"> Purchasing options </a> </span> </p>                <p class="a-text-italic"> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-buying-options-action" data-pqv-buying-options-action="{}"> <a id="pqv-buying-options" data-target="#dynamic-aod-ingress-box" class="a-link-normal" href="?ref=dp_product_quick_view#dynamic-aod-ingress-box"> Other sellers </a> </span> </p> <p class="a-text-italic"> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-unqualified-buybox-action" data-pqv-unqualified-buybox-action="{}"> <a id="pqv-unqualified-buybox" data-target="#unqualifiedBuyBox" class="a-link-normal" href="?ref=dp_product_quick_view#unqualifiedBuyBox"> Other sellers </a> </span> </p>  </div>         <div id="pqv-feature-bullets" data-target="#featurebullets_feature_div" class="a-section a-spacing-medium"> <h2 id="pqv-feature-bullets-heading">About this Item</h2> <ul class="a-unordered-list a-vertical">  <li><span class="a-list-item">Spring is coloured from one end to the other in the colours of the rainbow creating a fun multicoloured shimmering effect when played with.</span></li>  <li><span class="a-list-item">Coil is 6 cm tall when resting, 6.5cm diameter.</span></li>  <li><span class="a-list-item">Box Size: 7x7x7 cm</span></li>  </ul> </div>           <div id="pqv-description" data-target="#productDescription_feature_div" class="a-section a-spacing-medium">  <h2 id="pqv-description-heading">Product description</h2>    <div>
                    Spring is colored from one end to the other in the colors of the rainbow creating a fun multicolored shimmering effect when played with. Coil is 6cm tall when resting, 6.5cm diameter. Box Size: 7x7x7 cm.  </div>
               </div>                        <div class="a-section a-spacing-medium"> <h2 id="pqv-options-available">Options Available</h2>    <h3>Size</h3> <ul class="a-unordered-list a-vertical">  <li><span class="a-list-item"> pack of 2 </span></li>  </ul>  <h3>Colour</h3> <ul class="a-unordered-list a-vertical">  <li><span class="a-list-item"> Multi Coloured </span></li>  <li><span class="a-list-item"> Transparent. </span></li>  </ul>  <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-twister-action" data-pqv-twister-action="{}"> <a id="pqv-twister" data-target="#twister-plus-inline-twister,#twister" class="a-link-normal" href="?ref=dp_product_quick_view#twister"> Browse all available options </a> </span> </div>              <div id="pqv-important-information" data-target="#importantInformation_feature_div" class="a-section a-spacing-medium"> <h2 id="pqv-important-information-heading">Important Information</h2>    <h3>Safety Information:</h3>    <p>for Age 3+ </p>       <h3>Toy Safety</h3>   <p><ol class="a-ordered-list a-vertical"><li><span class="a-list-item">Our recommended age:  </span></li><li><span class="a-list-item">Manufacturer&#39;s minimum age: 14 years  </span></li><li><span class="a-list-item"> </span></li></ol></p>    <h3>header_for_buffet</h3>   <h2>Regulatory Information </h2><p>To know the product(s) that require Bureau of Indian Standards (BIS) Marking, please refer to  <a class="a-link-normal" href="https://www.bis.gov.in/product-certification/products-under-compulsory-certification/?ref=dp_product_quick_view">&#34;Mandatory certifications in India&#34; </a> or search using  <a class="a-link-normal" href="https://www.services.bis.gov.in/php/BIS_2.0/bisconnect/knowyourstandards/indian_standards/isdetails?ref=dp_product_quick_view">&#34;Know your standards&#34; </a></p>    </div>                  <div class="a-section a-spacing-medium"> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-report-issue-action" data-pqv-report-issue-action="{}"> <a id="pqv-report-issue" data-target="#tellAmazon_feature_div" class="a-link-normal" href="?ref=dp_product_quick_view#tellAmazon_feature_div"> Report an issue with this product or seller </a> </span> </div>                     <div id="pqv-feedback" class="a-section a-spacing-medium"> <h2 id="pqv-feedback-heading">Feedback</h2> <p>Did you find this product summary feature useful?</p>   <div id="pqv-feedback-buttons-section" class="a-section"> <div class="a-section a-padding-base aok-float-left"> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-feedback-positive-action" data-pqv-feedback-positive-action="{}"> <span id="pqv-feedback-positive" class="a-button a-button-base"><span class="a-button-inner"><input id="pqv-feedback-positive-native" aria-described-by="Submit feedback that this product summary is useful" class="a-button-input" type="submit" aria-labelledby="pqv-feedback-positive-announce"/><span id="pqv-feedback-positive-announce" class="a-button-text" aria-hidden="true"> Yes, it is useful </span></span></span> </span> </div> <div class="a-section a-padding-base"> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-feedback-negative-action" data-pqv-feedback-negative-action="{}"> <span id="pqv-feedback-negative" class="a-button a-button-base"><span class="a-button-inner"><input id="pqv-feedback-negative-native" aria-described-by="Submit feedback that this product summary isn't useful" class="a-button-input" type="submit" aria-labelledby="pqv-feedback-negative-announce"/><span id="pqv-feedback-negative-announce" class="a-button-text" aria-hidden="true"> No, it is not useful </span></span></span> </span> </div> </div> <div id="pqv-feedback-submit-section" class="a-section aok-hidden"> <div class="a-section a-padding-base aok-float-left"> <div class="a-box a-alert-inline a-alert-inline-success aok-hidden" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"><div class="a-box-inner a-alert-container"><i class="a-icon a-icon-alert" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="a-alert-content"> Thank you for your feedback </div></div></div> <div id="pqv-feedback-message-positive" class="a-box a-alert-inline a-alert-inline-success aok-hidden" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"><div class="a-box-inner a-alert-container"><i class="a-icon a-icon-alert" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="a-alert-content"> Thank you for your feedback. You selected “Yes, it is useful” </div></div></div> <div id="pqv-feedback-message-negative" class="a-box a-alert-inline a-alert-inline-success aok-hidden" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"><div class="a-box-inner a-alert-container"><i class="a-icon a-icon-alert" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="a-alert-content"> Thank you for your feedback. You selected “No, it is not useful” </div></div></div> </div> <div class="a-section a-padding-base"> <span class="a-declarative" data-action="pqv-feedback-reset-action" data-pqv-feedback-reset-action="{}"> <span id="pqv-feedback-reset" class="a-button a-button-base aok-hidden"><span class="a-button-inner"><input id="pqv-feedback-reset-native" class="a-button-input" type="submit" aria-labelledby="pqv-feedback-reset-announce"/><span id="pqv-feedback-reset-announce" class="a-button-text" aria-hidden="true"> Change your feedback </span></span></span> </span> </div> </div>    </div>  <div class="a-section a-spacing-medium"> <hr aria-hidden="true" class="a-divider-normal"/> <footer>
